{"tid":1557152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「美軍來了我帶路」九一四召集數萬名在港美國人舉行反共大集會","createTime":"2019-09-10T04:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T05:11:25.000Z","uid":150842,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f5a68b02c6f66b2e5127fa5057f5d9f088506bf6","tid":1557152,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:05:08.000Z","msg":"雖然一直以來講美國戰線都有啲距離，只限於網上平台接觸佢地做文宣，但點解大家冇諗到仲有在港美國人呢條戰線？既然要urge到美國國會做野，在港美國人顯然會更有say <br />\n一直以來都有意無意地忽略佢地參與既重要性，佢地都缺乏相當既渠道認知發生緊咩事，所以呢個集會係勢在必行，為九一五民集會造勢<br />\n我建議可以搵學界搞返次全英文集會，唱下美國國歌，扯美國旗！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89kUmRj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89kUmRj.jpg&h=2462eabe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b648b411b04911ccb9aca7106f381676e43c3fed","tid":1557152,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:05:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"581e5e838838474d50cfa566c682b401b0f8499b","tid":1557152,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:05:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5817a8edce709db3e991ded04273a620e96cdd5c","tid":1557152,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:06:02.000Z","msg":"如果行得通 請推我"},{"pid":"1ebf962b1e57c3dd5ddb0b54447c1b65fe3da7cf","tid":1557152,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:06:13.000Z","msg":"如果行得通 請推我"},{"pid":"295596622761b77f17c7af2928fc24e354296c89","tid":1557152,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:06:23.000Z","msg":"如果行得通 請推我"},{"pid":"97d01b98dfdb51433ebe5990f48b3616caa66fb1","tid":1557152,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:06:33.000Z","msg":"如果行得通 請推我"},{"pid":"4ac5d30ce0058815adc6b7aaae46a024e7343fbb","tid":1557152,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:07:09.000Z","msg":"如果行得通 請推我"},{"pid":"4ed5130cd4e157bd0ccaa8bf5c72d